snippet.title: Fable: Pre-Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
Check out a new look at Fable gameplay from Playground Games revealed by Craig Duncan, Head of Xbox Game Studios, on the Official Xbox Podcast. Duncan also revealed that Fable’s release date is now 2026.

Fable is the reimagining of the fantasy RPG series. Full of magic, fairytale characters, and signature humor, coming to Xbox Series X, Series S, and PC in 2026.

Fable is coming to Game Pass, Xbox Series X/S, and PC in 2026.

#IGN #Gaming #Fable
